{"tid":1725633,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《支那01》愛國藝人馬蹄露微博曬傷疤　內地網民送安慰：你從來不是靠外表！","createTime":"2019-11-15T20:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T00:23:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":190,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"91201212d9a9347a8684d6b0c09c7f8a781619a0","tid":1725633,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:37:21.000Z","msg":"獲《人民日報》在微博高度表揚的馬蹄露於上月初在旺角示威現場與示威者發生衝突，結果被噴紅油及嘴角受傷流血。日前，她就在微博曬出疤痕，更講道：「面上贈（增）添兩度疤痕，還有一道在下巴底部，化妝也可蓋得住，頭頂的那一道我看不到它！」<br />\n正在與歐陽震華和萬綺雯等人拍攝TVB警匪片《伙記辦大事》的她上月底已經早早復工，內地人氣更加如日沖天堪比一線明星。對於她臉上的疤痕，不少內地網民都給予她溫暖的安慰，紛紛留言：「馬蹄來大陸拍戲。」、「以前怎麼就沒覺得你這麼美麗。原諒我曾經瞎了眼。」和「你從來都不是靠外表而美。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3560635/org/2328b2e8bff8f92219047bbb4fdba3b1.jpg/8sJ68zzTGIPNsv6117yearLuXmRfdmPKmtKBtZrSgbU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3560635%2Forg%2F2328b2e8bff8f92219047bbb4fdba3b1.jpg%2F8sJ68zzTGIPNsv6117yearLuXmRfdmPKmtKBtZrSgbU&h=ce1d73b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/398837/%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E9%A6%AC%E8%B9%84%E9%9C%B2%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E6%9B%AC%E5%82%B7%E7%96%A4-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E9%80%81%E5%AE%89%E6%85%B0-%E4%BD%A0%E5%BE%9E%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E9%9D%A0%E5%A4%96%E8%A1%A8#media_id=3560635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F398837%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B9%2584%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A%25E6%259B%25AC%25E5%2582%25B7%25E7%2596%25A4-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%2585%25B0-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%259D%25A0%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25A1%25A8%23media_id%3D3560635&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA